author: Reuters
title: ICT Automatisering and Transparix develop cloud-based platform WebShipper.com
text:
Sept 1 ICT Automatisering NV :
* ICT and Transparix develop cloud-based platform WebShipper.com
* Have concluded a partnership to jointly launch the online cloud-based platform WebShipper.com (Gdynia Newsroom)
